    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a linear power band that breathes through a stock exhaust system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a functional M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring tactile engagement and mechanical grip. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to mitigate floor fatigue, and the dual-VANOS unit has been serviced with upgraded seals. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers for precise rebound characteristics. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals are strong, with documented rod bearing replacement and a recent valve adjustment. A technically sound specimen optimized for the purist driver.",
