      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW X5 xDrive35i is a standout example of luxury and performance, maintained with care and presented in impressive condition. The Alpine White exterior maintains a brilliant shine, showing only the slight, expected character marks consistent with responsible daily use. Inside, the Mocha Dakota leather cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the seats are supple, the carpets are clean, and the interior has been kept strictly smoke-free. Every feature, from the wide-screen navigation and panoramic sunroof to the multi-zone climate control, operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the 3.0L turbocharged engine delivers smooth, effortless power, paired with a transmission that shifts seamlessly. With a complete service history and tires that show deep tread, this vehicle is mechanically sound and ready for the road. It represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, premium SUV that has been treated with respect by its previous owner.",
